                <div class="badge-total">🛍️ 쇼핑몰(N샵, 쿠팡 등) · 총 <span id="openTotal">0</span>건</div>
                <div class="table-wrapper"><table><thead><tr><th>업체명</th><th>플랫폼</th><th>카테고리</th><th>전화번호</th></tr></thead><tbody id="openTbody"></tbody></table></div>
